{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"库存微服务 API","description":"专业的库存管理微服务，支持高并发环境下的库存安全管理，防止超卖问题。\n\n## 🚀 核心特性\n\n- **防超卖保障** - PostgreSQL 行级锁 + Redis 分布式锁双重保护\n- **高性能缓存** - Redis 缓存层加速读取，支持批量操作\n- **多层架构** - API / Celery / CLI 三种调用方式\n- **完整审计** - 详细的操作日志和状态追踪\n- **幂等保证** - 基于 Redis 的请求去重机制\n- **优雅降级** - Redis 故障时自动降级到数据库模式\n\n## 📚 文档说明\n\n- **基础路径**: `/api/v1`\n- **健康检查**: `GET /health`\n- **API 文档**: `GET /docs` (Swagger UI)\n- **ReDoc 文档**: `GET /redoc` (ReDoc UI)\n\n## 🔧 错误码说明\n\n- `200`: 请求成功\n- `400`: 请求参数错误\n- `404`: 资源未找到\n- `422`: 请求验证失败\n- `429`: 请求过于频繁\n- `500`: 服务器内部错误\n\n## 🌐 当前运行端口：8000\n如果端口被占用，系统将自动尝试使用其他可用端口。\n","termsOfService":"https://example.com/terms/","contact":{"name":"库存微服务团队","url":"https://github.com/your-org/inventory-service","email":"inventory@example.com"},"license":{"name":"MIT License","url":"https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT"},"version":"1.0.0"},"servers":[{"url":"http://localhost:8000/api/v1","description":"开发环境"},{"url":"https://api.example.com/api/v1","description":"生产环境"}],"paths":{"/api/v1/inventory/reserve":{"post":{"tags":["库存管理"],"summary":"预占库存","description":"预占指定商品的库存数量，防止超卖。\n    \n    **特点：**\n    - 使用数据库行级锁确保原子性\n    - 支持分布式锁防止并发冲突\n    - 15分钟后自动过期\n    - 幂等性保证\n    \n    **使用场景：**\n    - 用户下单时预占库存\n    - 购物车结算时锁定商品","operationId":"reserve_stock_api_v1_inventory_reserve_post","parameters":[{"name":"product_id","in":"query","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","exclusiveMinimum":0,"description":"商品 ID","examples":[1],"title":"Product Id"},"description":"商品 ID"},{"name":"quantity","in":"query","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","exclusiveMinimum":0,"description":"预占数量","examples":[2],"title":"Quantity"},"description":"预占数量"},{"name":"order_id","in":"query","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","minLength":1,"maxLength":64,"description":"订单 ID","examples":["ORD202401010001"],"title":"Order Id"},"description":"订单 ID"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"预占成功","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/OperationResponse"},"example":{"success":true,"message":"预占成功","data":true}}}},"400":{"description":"库存不足或重复预占","content":{"application/json":{"examples":{"insufficient_stock":{"summary":"库存不足","value":{"success":false,"message":"库存不足"}},"duplicate_reservation":{"summary":"重复预占","value":{"success":false,"message":"该订单已预占此商品"}}}}}},"404":{"description":"资源未找到"},"422":{"description":"请求验证失败"},"429":{"description":"请求过于频繁"},"500":{"description":"服务器内部错误"}}}},"/api/v1/inventory/confirm/{order_id}":{"post":{"tags":["库存管理"],"summary":"确认库存扣减","description":"确认预占的库存，实际扣减商品库存。\n    \n    **使用场景：**\n    - 用户支付成功后确认订单\n    - 系统自动确认超时订单\n    \n    **注意：**\n    - 只能确认状态为RESERVED的预占记录\n    - 确认后预占状态变为CONFIRMED","operationId":"confirm_stock_api_v1_inventory_confirm__order_id__post","parameters":[{"name":"order_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"订单 ID","examples":["ORD202401010001"],"title":"Order Id"},"description":"订单 ID"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"确认成功","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/OperationResponse"},"example":{"success":true,"message":"确认成功","data":true}}}},"400":{"description":"请求参数错误"},"404":{"description":"未找到有效的预占记录","content":{"application/json":{"example":{"success":false,"message":"未找到有效的预占记录"}}}},"422":{"description":"请求验证失败"},"429":{"description":"请求过于频繁"},"500":{"description":"服务器内部错误"}}}},"/api/v1/inventory/release/{order_id}":{"post":{"tags":["库存管理"],"summary":"释放预占库存","description":"释放预占的库存，归还给可用库存。\n    \n    **使用场景：**\n    - 用户取消订单\n    - 订单超时未支付\n    - 系统自动释放过期预占\n    \n    **效果：**\n    - 增加可用库存\n    - 减少预占库存\n    - 更新预占状态为RELEASED","operationId":"release_stock_api_v1_inventory_release__order_id__post","parameters":[{"name":"order_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"订单 ID","examples":["ORD202401010001"],"title":"Order Id"},"description":"订单 ID"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"释放成功","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/OperationResponse"},"example":{"success":true,"message":"释放成功","data":true}}}},"400":{"description":"请求参数错误"},"404":{"description":"未找到有效的预占记录","content":{"application/json":{"example":{"success":false,"message":"未找到有效的预占记录"}}}},"422":{"description":"请求验证失败"},"429":{"description":"请求过于频繁"},"500":{"description":"服务器内部错误"}}}},"/api/v1/inventory/cleanup/manual":{"post":{"tags":["库存管理"],"summary":"Manual Cleanup","description":"手动触发清理任务（方式二：API 直接调用 Service）","operationId":"manual_cleanup_api_v1_inventory_cleanup_manual_post","parameters":[{"name":"batch_size","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","default":500,"title":"Batch Size"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"400":{"description":"请求参数错误"},"404":{"description":"资源未找到"},"422":{"description":"请求验证失败"},"429":{"description":"请求过于频繁"},"500":{"description":"服务器内部错误"}}}},"/api/v1/inventory/cleanup/celery":{"post":{"tags":["库存管理"],"summary":"Celery Cleanup","description":"触发 Celery 异步清理任务（方式三：Celery 调用）","operationId":"celery_cleanup_api_v1_inventory_cleanup_celery_post","parameters":[{"name":"batch_size","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","default":500,"title":"Batch Size"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"400":{"description":"请求参数错误"},"404":{"description":"资源未找到"},"422":{"description":"请求验证失败"},"429":{"description":"请求过于频繁"},"500":{"description":"服务器内部错误"}}}},"/api/v1/inventory/cleanup/status/{task_id}":{"get":{"tags":["库存管理"],"summary":"Get Cleanup Status","description":"查询 Celery 任务执行状态","operationId":"get_cleanup_status_api_v1_inventory_cleanup_status__task_id__get","parameters":[{"name":"task_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Task Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"400":{"description":"请求参数错误"},"404":{"description":"资源未找到"},"422":{"description":"请求验证失败"},"429":{"description":"请求过于频繁"},"500":{"description":"服务器内部错误"}}}},"/api/v1/inventory/stock/{product_id}":{"get":{"tags":["库存管理"],"summary":"查询商品库存","description":"查询指定商品的可用库存数量。\n    \n    **缓存策略：**\n    - 首先查询Redis缓存\n    - 缓存未命中则查询数据库\n    - 查询结果缓存5分钟\n    \n    **性能优化：**\n    - 90%+的请求可直接从缓存获取\n    - 响应时间通常小于50ms","operationId":"get_stock_api_v1_inventory_stock__product_id__get","parameters":[{"name":"product_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","exclusiveMinimum":0,"description":"商品 ID","examples":[1],"title":"Product Id"},"description":"商品 ID"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"查询成功","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/StockResponse"},"example":{"success":true,"product_id":1,"available_stock":100}}}},"400":{"description":"请求参数错误"},"404":{"description":"资源未找到"},"422":{"description":"请求验证失败"},"429":{"description":"请求过于频繁"},"500":{"description":"服务器内部错误"}}}},"/api/v1/inventory/stock/batch":{"post":{"tags":["库存管理"],"summary":"批量查询商品库存","description":"批量查询多个商品的库存数量。\n    \n    **优势：**\n    - 单次请求查询多个商品\n    - Redis管道优化批量操作\n    - 减少网络往返次数\n    \n    **限制：**\n    - 单次最多查询100个商品\n    - 建议按业务场景合理分批","operationId":"batch_get_stocks_api_v1_inventory_stock_batch_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/BatchStockQueryRequest","description":"批量查询请求参数"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"批量查询成功","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/BatchStockResponse"},"example":{"success":true,"data":{"1":100,"2":50,"3":0}}}}},"400":{"description":"请求参数错误"},"404":{"description":"资源未找到"},"422":{"description":"请求验证失败"},"429":{"description":"请求过于频繁"},"500":{"description":"服务器内部错误"}}}},"/health":{"get":{"summary":"健康检查","description":"检查服务是否正常运行","operationId":"health_check_health_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"服务健康","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"additionalProperties":true,"type":"object","title":"Response Health Check Health Get"},"example":{"status":"healthy","service":"inventory-microservice","version":"1.0.0"}}}}}}},"/":{"get":{"summary":"API 根路径","description":"API 服务的根路径信息","operationId":"read_root__get","responses":{"200":{"description":"成功返回","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"additionalProperties":true,"type":"object","title":"Response Read Root  Get"},"example":{"message":"欢迎使用库存微服务","docs":"/docs","health":"/health"}}}}}}},"/config":{"get":{"summary":"服务配置信息","description":"返回当前服务的配置信息，包括端口、主机等，方便前端动态获取连接地址","operationId":"get_config_config_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"成功返回","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"additionalProperties":true,"type":"object","title":"Response Get Config Config Get"},"example":{"host":"0.0.0.0","port":8000,"api_base_url":"http://localhost:8000/api/v1","docs_url":"/docs","debug":true}}}}}}}},"components":{"schemas":{"BatchStockQueryRequest":{"properties":{"product_ids":{"items":{"type":"integer"},"type":"array","maxItems":100,"minItems":1,"title":"Product Ids","description":"商品ID列表","example":[1,2,3]}},"type":"object","required":["product_ids"],"title":"BatchStockQueryRequest","description":"批量查询库存请求"},"BatchStockResponse":{"properties":{"success":{"type":"boolean","title":"Success","description":"请求是否成功"},"message":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Message","description":"响应消息"},"data":{"additionalProperties":{"type":"integer"},"type":"object","title":"Data","description":"商品ID到库存数量的映射"}},"type":"object","required":["success","data"],"title":"BatchStockResponse","description":"批量库存查询响应"},"OperationResponse":{"properties":{"success":{"type":"boolean","title":"Success","description":"请求是否成功"},"message":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Message","description":"响应消息"},"data":{"anyOf":[{"type":"boolean"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Data","description":"操作结果"}},"type":"object","required":["success"],"title":"OperationResponse","description":"操作响应（预占、确认、释放）"},"StockResponse":{"properties":{"success":{"type":"boolean","title":"Success","description":"请求是否成功"},"message":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Message","description":"响应消息"},"product_id":{"type":"integer","title":"Product Id","description":"商品ID"},"available_stock":{"type":"integer","minimum":0.0,"title":"Available Stock","description":"可用库存数量"}},"type":"object","required":["success","product_id","available_stock"],"title":"StockResponse","description":"单个商品库存响应"}}},"tags":[{"name":"库存管理","description":"库存预占、确认、释放等核心操作"},{"name":"库存查询","description":"库存数量查询接口"},{"name":"任务管理","description":"清理任务和异步任务管理"}]}